column5: Well I found another one of those puzzle games. Now I'm stuck in the stairwell and can't figure it out.  Anyone dare to try this one? It was easier then the sphere one so far.  LOL  http://mirror8.cgdc2.fizzlebot.com/?puzzleID=2
LOL....where were these games 8 weeks ago when it was -20C out there?  Could have made the winter go by more quickly!!!
